title: Project Open PS(P)3   [DHT works now]
description:
Hello, we worked on Project Open PS(P)3 but we now give up (for now).

This project is about to convert&run PSP games on consoles PS3 .


Thic pack contains (2.13 GB):

- 4 games, 2 normal psp and 2 minis psp.
- many tools, programs
- screens+ wideo from our tests
- PSP SDK
- some converted/encrypted eboots, param.fso, disc.sfb from both consoles psp+ps3 etc.
- many more..
